{"tid":2197254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#426：網上交易，提防詐騙","createTime":"2020-09-10T12:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T18:24:16.000Z","uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f75b1b2e5e8750a8429220c9de120e06e33e45","tid":2197254,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"center\"><br />\nLIHK乃PO呼籲:<br />\n一日警察署長鈴木絢音呼籲<br />\n網上交易，提防詐騙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOOGJTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOOGJTi.jpg&h=0c68ab2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一至四期生在內，團體目前共有48名成員，而隊長為秋元真夏。其與2015年8月21日成立的櫸坂46、以及2019年2月11日自櫸坂46獨立的日向坂46，構成大型偶像組合系列「坂道系列」。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團名取自坐落東京都赤坂地區乃木坂的「SME乃木坂大樓」，該建築為所屬唱片公司日本索尼音樂的前辦公大樓之一。根據秋元康所說，<span class=\"red\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"purple\"><p class=\"center\">-NEWS-</p></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\"><br />\n白石麻衣 乃木坂46卒業記念メモリアルマガジン<br />\n<span class=\"red\">10月21日</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHCnCi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHCnCi1.jpg&h=4c25a4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMusic Video集「ALL MV COLLECTION２～あの時の彼女たち～」<br />\n<span class=\"red\">發売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVnMD8R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVnMD8R.jpg&h=27787ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\"><br />\n乃木坂46 配信限定曲『Route 246』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCoH77V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCoH77V.jpg&h=6e68d9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中田花奈1st写真集<br />\n<span class=\"red\">10月13日発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S46Lz32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS46Lz32.jpg&h=df6d78ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梅澤美波1st写真集『夢の近く』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">9月29日発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://actresspress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1957975392d55b468f43956447ce3587-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Factresspress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F1957975392d55b468f43956447ce3587-scaled.jpg&h=bb76d3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n与田祐希 2nd写真集『無口な時間』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">發売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp/@0_mall/book/cabinet/9619/2100011829619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp%2F%400_mall%2Fbook%2Fcabinet%2F9619%2F2100011829619.jpg&h=f3c7875e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秋元真夏2nd写真集『しあわせにしたい』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E09mMtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE09mMtJ.jpg&h=fb4bd72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堀未央奈2nd写真集『いつかの待ち合わせ場所』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kCZaTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kCZaTy.jpg&h=90f8cb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p></span><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">乃木坂46成員列表（最新）</span></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiwFp7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiwFp7s.jpg&h=a613c338&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEdDWed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEdDWed.jpg&h=2ee64564&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOdMkF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOdMkF0.jpg&h=772b3c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WnYbNH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WnYbNH.jpg&h=89f903c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYFCsk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYFCsk5.jpg&h=1e5a7602&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fnogizaka46sort.html&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=fb418b97\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html</a></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">請新/舊手足定期體檢</span></p><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\">Q&amp;A</p></span></span><br />\n</p><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...不如幫襯某良心代購小店，詳情請向手足查詢。另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員，但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本<del>或中國</del>參加握手會、演唱會、見面會，但不要幻想會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n網上購物，唔識就問，小心做水魚呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"32b7228c70fd870525a0f0c5357b331c76261a1a","tid":2197254,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"乃木坂46討論區#426：吉田綾乃クリスティー生日快樂!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2190357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2190357</a>"},{"pid":"61506f73aa33edf6483764ae37cff7d45c0b6827","tid":2197254,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"拉哂你班罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jV2DL8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjV2DL8w.jpg&h=8b42d65d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1162d6054f1f9ebbe6aa85403d9a71c64944b742","tid":2197254,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3d7941820cfe944f77d8b4b6d8d500ac1e22ff","tid":2197254,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:59:05.000Z","msg":"仆街　冇改期數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df5c5422d5d65b7882b8fe343932ba57a44159d","tid":2197254,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"427<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba741ab410b875ea9c7f626dc1eb8f6d10c6a4c","tid":2197254,"uid":189666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"柒左  對唔字大佬"},{"pid":"7c1cfd0311d8b40737e5b98dd6c10927bbbb3817","tid":2197254,"uid":207542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"SIU4"},{"pid":"aa79068e2a4ebbd08a94f581706ee9bebdec3886","tid":2197254,"uid":229106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}